quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  70,11,"Hi…ďe kollindiree. Bon…óo on yeloto sottorde lepte …óen nden √Īande, …ďi…ó…ďe makko …ďeen."
  70,12,"e gennda makko, e musi…ó…óo neene gooto makko on."
  70,13,"E gorol makko ngol moolatngol mo."
  70,14,"e kala won…ďe e lesdi …ďeen, fii no …óuum da…óndira mo."
  70,15,"∆äuum gasataa. Ngen [Yiite] ko uuyunge,"
  70,16,"…ďoltatnge guri hoore."
  70,17,"Henge nodda oon …óuurnii…óo o ruŇčiti,"
  70,18,"o moo…ďi (jaw…óe) o mari e marirgel."
  70,19,"Pellet, ne…ó…óo o tagaama ko o …óen∆īotoo…óo;"
  70,20,"si bone memi mo, o faaya."
  70,21,"Si ko mo mo∆ī∆īere nde he…ďi mo, o salora."
  70,22,"Si wonaa juuloo…ďe …ďeen."
  70,23,"…ďeen taw…ďe ko …ďe duumii…ďe e juulde ma…ď…ďe ndeen."
  70,24,"E …ďeen taw…ďe hino ka jaw…óe ma…ď…ďe haqqee ganndaa…óo,"
  70,25,"wonan'de torotoo…óo e …óawaa…óo."
  70,26,"e E …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe √Īalaande njo…ďdi nde,"
  70,27,"E …ďeen taw…ďe ko …ďe hulu…ďe lepte Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen"
  70,28,"Tawde pellet, lepte Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen ngonaa koolnii…óe,"
  70,29,"E …ďeen taw…ďe ko reen…ďe farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óiin"
  70,30,"si wonaa e rew…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa …ďeen hor…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďe …ďe jeyiri √Īaame ma…ď…ďe, …óoon on …ďe peletaake."
  70,31,"Kala noon …óa…ď…ďu…óo [ka dakmitora] caggal …óuum, haray ko …ďeen ngoni jaggitu…ďe …ďeen."
  70,32,"E …ďeen taw…ďe ko aynitu…ďe koolaaje e aadiiji ma…ď…ďe …óiin."
  70,33,"E …ďeen taw…ďe ko √Īii…ďu…ďe e seedeeji mum."
  70,34,"E …ďeen taw…ďe ko reenoo…ďe e juulde ma…ď…ďe ndeen."
  70,35,"∆Āeen …óoon ko teddinoytee…ďe e aljannaaji."
  70,36,"E ko he…ďi yeddu…ďe …ďeen takko maa…óa, he…ďe ke√Īora."
  70,37,"To nano e ka √Īaamo, ko …ďe dento√Ī-dento√Ī?"
  70,38,"Hara go'oto kala e ma…ď…ďe tam∆īinoto naatoygol aljanna ne'emaaji?"
  70,39,"∆äum wa…óataa ! Min tagiri…ďe ko …ďe nganndi."